title: Samsung Galaxy Note 2 AT&T SGH-I317 Stock Firmware
description:
This is the Samsung Galaxy Note 2 AT&T SGH-I317 Stock Firmware. The reason I posted this torrent is that most sites that host this are terribly slow.

It can be used in conjunction with the Galaxy Note 2 Toolkit @ http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=1923956

If you have Cyanogenmod or another custom ROM and would like to revert or just troubleshoot (like I did) this can help.

The name of this version of firmware is I317UCALJ2_ATT, hope it helps.
